1st year mein toh mere liye tu vo ladka tha jiska pehle ghr NCL hai aur dusra wingðŸ˜‚.Phir 2nd year se tere saath baatein shuru hui.phir apna goa vaala trip aur usme rafting Vaala incident toh hmesha yaad rhega kaise ek baar teri phti aur upar aakr bol rha maza aaya maza aayaðŸ˜‚aur doosra "matlabi toh sb hote hai".phir toh apna roomie banana(by the way tu bhot shi roomie tha yr).haan maana thoda rondu zyada haiðŸ˜… pr tune kbhi help krne ke liye mana ni kiya.

text:
Aur missu Dhep! 
Bhai first year tk toh mein bs tujhe aise hi jaanta tha ki hmari wing ka ek banda hai jo wing se zyada baki wings mein zyada rehta haiðŸ˜‚.phir 2nd year se jb tu Ritesh ka roomie bna toh uske baad se hmari baatein shuru hui.uske baad toh jb bhi tere saath jata canteen kbhi 1ghnte se pehle ni aataðŸ˜‚.baki tera chillana bhot yaad aayega abhi bhi bokaro mein chillata hai toh punjab awaaz aati hai ðŸ˜‚.Aur ek baat yaad rkhna carrom,football,cards mein tu bachcha hi rhega ðŸ˜›.
author: Rahul  Jindal

text:
Aur bhai shukla!
Bhaiyon ko chodkr tu hi tha jo mera pehla dost bna tha campus mein.uske baad toh bs phir roz raat ko canteen jana ho,raat ko rolls khane oat jana ho,late night talks,phir tere raat ke mood swings ko sambhalna hoðŸ˜‚.yaad hai ek raat jb doaa gye they paidal aur library ke paas kitte pr gye they piche kya toh phti thi yr.yaad hai 2nd year ki antragni toh pubg khelte nikali.ek hi baat ka dukh rhega tere saath trip miss ho gya.bhot maza aaya yr inn 4 saalon mein.abhi iss saal tu bhi acchi c placement le aur aaja apni city hi.
Jldi hi milenge.
author: Rahul  Jindal

text:
Aur bhaiyyyy pandeyyyy! ! 
 Mujhe yaad hai hum pehli baar TA202 mein mile they.vahan toh TA202 ke project ke ilawa zyada baatein ni ho paati pr yr ye 30 din jo guzre,vo tera roz ka wing mein ghoomte phirna bhai sutta hai sutta haiðŸ˜‚,bhookh lg rhi ,cards khelna subah tk breakfast ke liye jagna aise lgta tha jaise first year ke dost ho.dekhte hai abhi kya aati hai job location banglore aayi toh pelte hai yr vahan bakchodi.
author: Rahul  Jindal

text:
Aur bhai Ritesh!
Tere baare mein toh jitna bolu utna km hai yr.hum pehli baar physics ke tutorial mein mile they jb midden ke papers baant rhi thi tutor, vaise hi phti pdhi thi aur tujhse alg se himmat mil rhi thi jb tu keh rha tera bhi accha ni hua.vo alg baat hia vo bs 2 min ki hi thi himmat(samajh toh gya hi hoga tu)ðŸ˜‚ uske baad se toh yr phir chahe end sems ke liye padhna ho, koi bhi apni baatein share krni ho, football khelna ,phir chahe placement ke liye madad krni ho,tu best partner tha yr.aise hi na thodi na hmein love birds bolte theyðŸ˜‚.Aur vo mussoorie ki trip kaise bhool skte hai jahan choona lg wake kr aaye theyðŸ˜‚.bs ab ek hi baat ka dukh hai yr tu ab hyderabad ja rha aur hmara banglore mein football khelna ka plan reh gyaðŸ˜­.Ab lgta hai mujhe hi hyderabad aakr khelni pdhegi football.
author: Rahul  Jindal

text: Aur bhai motu(past ke liye).ab toh apne bhai ne dieting shuru kr di hai(fitness pro).hmari trip ka mastermind aur money bankðŸ˜‚.yaad hai George everest  jaate time tera bolte phirna thoda rukte hai na abhi thak gye hai.aur yr 2nd year ki summer mein jo roz shaam ko chat khane jana,phir hall 1 ki canteen.aur ipl mein teri opposite team ko cheer krne mein bhot maza aata tha aur aata rhega.
author: Rahul  Jindal

text:
Yo vijju boi!
Jb pehli baar kmre mein aaya tha tu toh lga tha bhai ye kaun aa gya pdhaku baccha.phir pta lga ye toh apni hi breed haiðŸ˜‚.1st year toh yr phir aisa hi nikala hai chl roll order krte hai,chl anime dekhte hai,aur sabse main chl Sanjay ki lete haiðŸ˜‚.Aur sbse main point jo aaj tk chl rha(chl WWE krte hai).kya majje kiye hai yr vo alg baat hai 2nd year se tu thoda zyada hi pdhaku bachcha bn gya tha(chaapu in coding).Ab toh apna bhai smart bhi ho gya hai.tere se toh milna hota rhega kahin bhi jaunga toh delhi hokr hi jaunga bs tu bed ka intezaam karke rkhna agla WWE delhi mein hi hoga.
author: Rahul  Jindal
